{"tid":126654,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"歷史學家大預言…川普注定短命總統","createTime":"2017-02-19T13:49:48.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-19T17:53:41.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5c7e12386df827aa43a69b9fe8a0df930dee6cde","tid":126654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:49:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/861n9kT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F861n9kT.jpg&h=7c3f504a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歷史學家費曼預言川普可能取代加菲爾德，成為美國第二短命總統。 法新社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國歷史學家兼作家費曼斷言美國總統川普的白宮歲月肯定短命，很可能在199天內鞠躬下台，成為美國史上在位時間第二短的總統。即使能拖得久一些，也很難超過16個月零5天，依然會成為在位時間第三短的總統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/19/214917_b93b935f0033446f50dfc0067bd99b55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F19%2F214917_b93b935f0033446f50dfc0067bd99b55.jpg&h=0280a87e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佛羅里達大西洋大學教授費曼（Ronald L Feinman）預言，川普待在白宮的日子應該介於1841年哈里遜總統的31天，與1881年加菲爾德總統的199天之間。哈里遜因受涼一病不起，撒手人寰。加菲爾德在遭槍擊暗殺79天後離世。<br />\n<br />\n即使川普拖過了一年半載，費曼預測，川普的白宮生涯不會比1850年總統泰勒還長，泰勒因消化毛病於在位16個月又5天後駕鶴西歸。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2293768?from=udn-hotnews_ch2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F10764%2F2293768%3Ffrom%3Dudn-hotnews_ch2&d=raogrMnRIgwaKnbVZhVJo%2F%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=104122a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/10764/2293768?from=udn-hotnews_ch2</a>"},{"pid":"f2be6f64cc4b601a58a5cea7ebff391fc4bbda81","tid":126654,"uid":35630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T13:54:00.000Z","msg":"rip"},{"pid":"b25d9472d2fb73b42b6193c4ff299ad5ae7633e6","tid":126654,"uid":14449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:04:29.000Z","msg":"學者得啖笑<br />\n侵應該會做夠8年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fc4490e43b5603e048decee441bb9bbfbdeee247","tid":126654,"uid":76470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:06:02.000Z","msg":"唔好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n侵侵仲要打巢終國同解決南海問題架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33c817caa0c566427cfe36e61b582e1556ff4462","tid":126654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:36:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"774c9400d7be40f599f995278da762e3bf7daa3f","tid":126654,"uid":41524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:45:59.000Z","msg":"等bin c啦"},{"pid":"bcc3dfc599365e23c44da3400325c9eb35da6221","tid":126654,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T14:46:22.000Z","msg":"鳩嗡學者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23c90c7810b04223abf3321b473362e245c9dcbb","tid":126654,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:51:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b1401b012c90bdd8f3714e7538bbd17883d97e5","tid":126654,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T16:52:35.000Z","msg":"啲預言家估中你咪叻 柒左咪潛水冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c66de228392ff0eadd30a63e042fcd00a01d36e","tid":126654,"uid":38049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:18:17.000Z","msg":"詛咒佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a8f47e438b5daa6c4766b5daf6f9001922e712e","tid":126654,"uid":43173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02